*''Loose Canon: A Portrait of Brian Brindley'' (ed) (Continuum, 2004);<ref>{{cite web|last=Knight|first=India|title=Like a fat blackbird|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/books/3620520/Like-a-fat-blackbird.html|publisher=''The Telegraph''|date=11 July 2004}}</ref> {{ISBN|9780826474186}}
